lpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Entrance of Celestica Inc. in Mississauga, Ontario, Canada\" data-id=\"1163638872\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4163px\" height=\"2775px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The last few years have shown just how critical a strong supply chain is, both for the biggest companies, and for individual consumers. The COVID-19 pandemic, the blockage of the Suez Canal, and a host of other events have caused enormous disruption</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1163638872/image_1163638872.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742977-celestica-could-be-tremendously-undervalued-as-pressures-grow-on-supply-chains", "pub_date": "2024-12-09 14:00:08"}, {"id": "4742983", "title": "Columbia Select Mid Cap Growth Fund Q3 2024 Commentary", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156898365/image_2156898365.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Investment and finance strategy for short-term and long-term profit. Businessman selecting best ROI and portfolio growth. Financial advisor guiding choices in the market managing risk and reward.\" data-id=\"2156898365\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156898365/image_2156898365.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156898365/image_2156898365.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156898365/image_2156898365.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156898365/image_2156898365.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156898365/image_2156898365.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156898365/image_2156898365.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156898365/image_2156898365.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2156898365/image_2156898365.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NicoElNino/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <span class=\"table-responsive\"><span class=\"table-scroll-wrapper\"><span data-intersection-boundar